      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARCTIC FLASH (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Curmudgeon (23.20) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to give a sight. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can go on with it. ZIPPER NIGHT (2) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only a neck from the winner Zipping Lombardi in second(23.74) at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Leading chance. BOTOX CHEVY (7) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at this track over 272m behind Super Skunk (16.65) in a Maiden. Was in the money the start prior. The form out of her last race has been franked. Worth another chance. STREET JUSTICE (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
